Package GoNature

Class Visit

  • java.lang.Object
    • GoNature.Visit
  • public class Visit
extends java.lang.Object
    The Visit class represents a visit to a park made by travelers. It contains details such as visit ID, park name, order type, number of visitors, entry time, and exit time. This class provides methods to retrieve and modify visit details.
    Author:
    Pier Mbariky, Redan Ganim, Bassel Haddad, Joel Hourany, Asaad Sajim
